        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为需要两个主要分组：客户端是LabAnalyzer，服务端是PatientRecords。诊断引擎在客户端侧，HIPAA Vault和EMR Sync分布在两侧对吗？",
