        "Server",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。客户端这边我准备放五个节点：C1到C5。C1和C5都是DiagnosticEngine，C2是HIPAA_Vault，C3和C4都是EMR_Sync。这样设计是为了展示重复实例的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "C5",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，客户端子图已创建，五个节点按您说的配置好了。C1和C5都是诊断引擎，C2是保险库，C3和C4是EMR同步节点。现在处理服务端？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
