      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务端六个节点S1到S6。S1和S4是HIPAA_Vault，S3和S5是DiagnosticEngine，S6是LabAnalyzer。注意S2要画成菱形，它是EMR_Sync的决策点，需要分支判断。",
